		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />If you just want to rip it for use in a graphics editor such as Photoshop, then open the ROM in question in a tile editor, press Alt+Print Screen to copy an image of the current window to the Clipboard, and paste it to the PC screen:
<br />
<br /><img src="http://pics.pineight.com/nes/smb1-font.png" alt="Image" />
<br />
<br />BTW, who had the copyright on that font? I'd bet the owner of that font could have made a wad of royalties.

		

