		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Not necessarily. I've been collecting 8x8 pixel fonts, and though the ones in Super Mario Bros., Tetris (Tengen), Tetris (Nintendo), and Lode Runner look rather similar, the one in the Mega Man series looks somewhat different, and the one used in Tetris for Game Boy is totally different.
<br />
<br /><img src="http://pics.pineight.com/nes/8x8s.png" alt="Image" />
<br /><strong>Figure 2:</strong> There's more than one way to make an 8x8 pixel font
<br />
